<eesti>(2) Vabariigi Valitsusel on &otilde;igus kehtestada n&otilde;uded autori&otilde;igusega kaasnevate &otilde;iguste teatud objektide k&auml;ibe dokumenteerimisele. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) The Government of the Republic has the right to establish requirements for documenting the circulation of certain objects of related rights. </inglise>
